answers.answer: Hi,How are you? Are there other symptoms present? Can you elaborate on the cyst present at the back of your head? Syncope or losing consciousness with nose bleeding may be related to the cyst, high blood pressure, eye and ear issues, and medical conditions such as anemia, diabetes and many others. You would benefit from direct clinical examination by your attending physician for proper evaluation.  Additional tests are also important to determine he underlying cause. Take care and hope to hear from you soon.
